# Keep lockfiles in repo for reproducible builds:
# Cargo.lock (binary crates) and package-lock.json are tracked.

# Generated Tauri schemas (local gen; may be recreated)
# src-tauri/gen/ is useful for some workflows; ignore heavy build only.
src-tauri/gen/schemas/*.json.bak

